  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u2013 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sanakyan and Sumanthran to build temple on Kurundur hill massive obstacle \u2013 laments Thera",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A video is being shared on the internet in which a Thera complains that Tamil National Federation Parliamentarians MA Sumanthran and Ira Sanakyan are facing massive obstacles in building a temple on Kurundur Hill.",
        "In the said video, \"The position of the Tamil National Federation is based on the principles of the Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam (LTTE).",
        "They say that there should be no Sinhalese in the North, they have no right. However, unfortunately everyone addresses the Parliament beautifully. They also mention that everyone should work together.",
        "Sumanthran and Chanakyan Rajamanickam have held talks with the protestors. They mention that the country should be developed, corruption should be eradicated and humane action should be taken.",
        "Humanitarian commentators do not pay attention to the preservation of archaeological monuments in the North.",
        "People benefit economically from archaeological sites in the south. Most of the archaeological remains are in the north.",
        "Over 600 archaeological sites have been identified so far. If the archaeological sites are developed in the north, the north will prosper economically.",
        "Why are the so-called Tamil leaders not cooperating with this? In the south they are commenting on one nation - one law, in the north they are commenting on separate Eelam and creating problems,\u201d said the Thera.",
        "\"Both of us are strongly protesting against various illegal activities in the North and East.",
        "In particular, we have taken action in connection with the illegal vicarage on Kurundur Hill. That is why this thera has taken the mudslinging action against us.",
        "At present, when all races are traveling together in Sri Lanka, there is a danger of ethnic harmony being affected by the activities of such few people."
      ],
